%% Diagram: Streaming SSR with Suspense
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Server as SSR Server
    participant Fast as Fast Data
    participant Slow as Slow Data

    Browser->>Server: GET /product/42
    Server-->>Browser: HTML shell + nav + Suspense fallbacks (TTFB)
    Note over Browser: Browser parses, renders shell\nFCP / LCP can already happen
    par Resolve in parallel
        Server->>Fast: query product info
        Fast-->>Server: 30 ms response
        Server-->>Browser: <script>$RC swaps fallback A
    and
        Server->>Slow: query recommendations
        Slow-->>Server: 400 ms response
        Server-->>Browser: <script>$RC swaps fallback B
    end
    Server-->>Browser: closes connection
    Note over Browser: Selective hydration\nattaches handlers per Suspense
